Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うう くたば れ
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop d—
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて諸君
